  "title": "feat(clearRefinements): implement InstantSearch.css",
  "body": "This PR updates clearAll to match our is.css specification.\r\n\r\n**Things done**\r\n\r\n - update name: clearAll -> clearRefinements\r\n - rename excludeAttributes -> excludedAttributes\r\n - update template keys\r\n - update css classes keys\r\n\r\nIt also adds\r\n\r\n - capability to pass an IS configuration in dev-novel for connector stories\r\n\r\n**Notes**\r\n\r\n - since the implementation is based on a button instead of a link, it simplifies the implementation of the component\r\n\r\n**Test**\r\n\r\n - [component](https://deploy-preview-3114--algolia-instantsearch.netlify.com/v2/dev-novel/?selectedStory=ClearRefinements.default)\r\n - [connector](https://deploy-preview-3114--algolia-instantsearch.netlify.com/v2/dev-novel/?widgets=jquery&selectedStory=ClearAll.default)",
